Introduction
-------------
This is a sample Sakai MyShowcase webapp. 
You will need version 2.6.2 of sakai or better to run this in.


Building the Webapp
-------------------
Build the app by running this command from the location of this README:
mvn clean install sakai:deploy

Start Sakai and you will see the new app appear as a tool option.
You will need to perform the data insert to initialise the database before you can use MyShowcase

Data Insert
-----------
Before using the sakai MyShowcase webapp, the MyShowcase database requires initialising.
The insert statements are included in the download and are located at:
SQL Resources/Scrips/myShowcaseDataInsert

Pre-Built myshowcase.war
------------------------
If you don't want to build the Sakai webapp, a ready built war file in included as part of the download.
Simply drop this into the webapps directory of your Sakai/Tomcat installation and perform the data insert.

